 hand to the base of his neck pulling forth a strange skin like mask dropping iton the ground. His hand raises up pulling two clay looking gums from his mouth dropping them on the mask. He then smoothed back his hair pulling his cloak up off of him. Revealing a small punctured water sack on his lap, pushing it off onto the ground. He sighes again looking around at the poeple. &quot;What a mess.. maybe it was a bad plan.. Ah doesn't matter now.&quot; He looks at Alysia shrugging slowly knowing he'll have to answer to her later. &quot;The shipment is from Octavius, I thought it may be a good gesture.  I came in disquise because I didn't know how Hera would think of me coming to her amazons. And an old man shouldn't be leading a transport from rome. Thanks for the greeting. And Aphrodite is here because hurting one of you is a death warrant is it not? And I was hoping she could.. maybe calm you or teleport you saftely away?&quot; <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=alastorofancients>Alastor of Ancients</A> at: 7/12/01 11:40:37 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ugoddessartemis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goddess Artemis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Goddess</span><br>  Posts: 99<br> <font color=#993300>(7/12/01 11:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=248.topic&index=62>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/mogoddessartemis/images/artemis2.bmp WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Revealing.</span><hr size=1> ~crosses her muscled arms over her chest~ Oh my dear boy, it most certainly is a death warrant, you've gotten that right.<br>
